    implementation_delta: |
      Cycle 017: LNG-CORE-62 marked complete - String escape sequences.

      Discovery: Implementation was already complete in grammar_contract.py.
      The _tokenize() function in grammar_contract.py already handles:
      - \\n -> newline (0x0A)
      - \\t -> tab (0x09)
      - \\" -> double quote
      - \\\\ -> single backslash
      - \\r -> carriage return (0x0D)

      Error handling:
      - E_PARSE_INVALID_ESCAPE for unsupported escapes (e.g., \\x, \\q, \\0)
      - E_PARSE_UNTERMINATED_STRING for unterminated strings
      - Error location includes line, column, and escape_char

      Tests: runtime/test_escape_sequences.py exists with comprehensive test coverage
      - Positive path: all 5 escape sequences
      - Negative path: invalid escapes, unterminated strings
      - Integration: escapes in concat, list, object contexts

      Commit: Synced evolution metadata files (meta: sync state files for LNG-CORE-62 completion)
    tests:
      - runtime/test_escape_sequences.py: passed
      - grammar_contract escape processing: verified
